text: Harry Prinzler (January 25, 1883 - December 25, 1952) was an American gymnast. He competed in three events at the 1904 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1883 births Category:1952 deaths Category:American male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of the United States Category:Gymnasts at the 1904 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Indianapolis
